\mt2 This book contains the account of Ezekiel foretelling about Jerusalem being destroyed and rebuilt. We call this book  
\mt1 Ezekiel  
\c 1  
\s1 Ezekiel saw Yahweh’s glory  
\p
\v 1-2  \add I am\add* Ezekiel, \w a|strong="H3068"\w* priest, the son of Buzi. When I was 30 years \add old\add*, I was\add living\add* among the\add Israeli\add* people who had been ◄exiled from/forced to leave► Judah\add and had come to Babylon\add*. I was living along the Kebar River/Canal\add south of Babylon\add*. Almost five years after King Jehoiachin had been ◄exiled/forced to leave Judah►, on the fifth day of the fourth month\add of that year, it was as though\add* the sky was opened and I saw visions from God.  
\p On that day,  
\v 3 \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w gave|strong="H1961"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w* \w messages|strong="H1697"\w*\add in visions here\add* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w Babylonia|strong="H3778"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* felt \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w power|strong="H3027"\w* [MTY] \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w*.   
\p
\v 4  \add In one of the visions, I saw a\add* windstorm \w coming|strong="H2009"\w* \w from|strong="H4480"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \w north|strong="H6828"\w*. \w There|strong="H2009"\w* \w was|strong="H7307"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* huge \w cloud|strong="H6051"\w*, \w and|strong="H1419"\w* lightning \w was|strong="H7307"\w* \w flashing|strong="H3947"\w* continually, \w and|strong="H1419"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* brilliant \w light|strong="H5051"\w* \w surrounded|strong="H5439"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \w cloud|strong="H6051"\w*. \w In|strong="H8432"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \w center|strong="H8432"\w* \w of|strong="H7307"\w* \w where|strong="H2009"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* lightning \w was|strong="H7307"\w* \w flashing|strong="H3947"\w* \w there|strong="H2009"\w* \w was|strong="H7307"\w* something \w that|strong="H7200"\w* resembled \w glowing|strong="H2830"\w* bronze.  
\v 5 \w In|strong="H8432"\w* \w the|strong="H8432"\w* \w center|strong="H8432"\w* \w of|strong="H8432"\w* \w the|strong="H8432"\w* storm \w I|strong="H2088"\w* \w saw|strong="H4758"\w* \w what|strong="H2088"\w* \w resembled|strong="H1823"\w* four \w living|strong="H2416"\w* \w creatures|strong="H2416"\w*. \w They|strong="H2007"\w* \w resembled|strong="H1823"\w* humans,  
\v 6 but \w each|strong="H3671"\w* \w of|strong="H6440"\w* \w them|strong="H6440"\w* had four \w faces|strong="H6440"\w* \w and|strong="H6440"\w* four \w wings|strong="H3671"\w* [DOU].  
\v 7 \w Their|strong="H7272"\w* \w legs|strong="H7272"\w* \w were|strong="H5869"\w* \w straight|strong="H3477"\w*. \w Their|strong="H7272"\w* \w feet|strong="H7272"\w* resembled \w the|strong="H5869"\w* hooves \w of|strong="H5869"\w* \w calves|strong="H5695"\w*, \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w the|strong="H5869"\w* creatures shone \w like|strong="H7272"\w* \w polished|strong="H7044"\w* \w bronze|strong="H5178"\w*.  
\v 8 \w On|strong="H5921"\w* \w their|strong="H6440"\w* four \w sides|strong="H7253"\w* \w under|strong="H8478"\w* \w their|strong="H6440"\w* \w wings|strong="H3671"\w* \w there|strong="H8478"\w* \w were|strong="H3027"\w* \w hands|strong="H3027"\w* \w like|strong="H8478"\w* humans \w have|strong="H3027"\w*.  
\v 9 \w As|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* four creatures\add stood there, they formed a circle/square\add*, \w with|strong="H6440"\w* \w their|strong="H6440"\w* \w wings|strong="H3671"\w* \w touching|strong="H2266"\w* \w each|strong="H3671"\w* \w other|strong="H5676"\w*. \w They|strong="H3808"\w* \w did|strong="H3808"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w turn|strong="H5437"\w* when \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w were|strong="H3671"\w* moving; \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w went|strong="H3212"\w* \w straight|strong="H5676"\w* \w ahead|strong="H6440"\w*.   
\p
\v 10 Each\add of the creatures had four faces\add*. \w The|strong="H6440"\w* \w face|strong="H6440"\w* \w that|strong="H5404"\w* \w was|strong="H6440"\w* \w in|strong="H6440"\w* \w front|strong="H6440"\w* \add of each one was a face that \add* \w resembled|strong="H1823"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* human \w face|strong="H6440"\w*. \w The|strong="H6440"\w* \w face|strong="H6440"\w* \w on|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w right|strong="H3225"\w* \w side|strong="H3225"\w* \w resembled|strong="H1823"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* lion’s \w face|strong="H6440"\w*. \w The|strong="H6440"\w* \w face|strong="H6440"\w* \w on|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w left|strong="H8040"\w* \w side|strong="H3225"\w* \w resembled|strong="H1823"\w* \w an|strong="H6440"\w* \w ox|strong="H7794"\w*’s \w face|strong="H6440"\w*. \w The|strong="H6440"\w* \w face|strong="H6440"\w* \w in|strong="H6440"\w* back \w resembled|strong="H1823"\w* \w an|strong="H6440"\w* \w eagle|strong="H5404"\w*’s \w face|strong="H6440"\w*.  
\v 11 \w Two|strong="H8147"\w* \w of|strong="H6440"\w* \w each|strong="H8147"\w* creature’s \w wings|strong="H3671"\w* \w were|strong="H3671"\w* lifted \w up|strong="H2266"\w* \w and|strong="H6440"\w* \w touched|strong="H2266"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w wings|strong="H3671"\w* \w of|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* creatures that \w were|strong="H3671"\w* \w on|strong="H6440"\w* \w each|strong="H8147"\w* \w side|strong="H8147"\w*. \w The|strong="H6440"\w* \w other|strong="H8147"\w* \w two|strong="H8147"\w* \w wings|strong="H3671"\w* \w were|strong="H3671"\w* folded \w against|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* creature’s \w body|strong="H1472"\w*.  
\v 12 \w The|strong="H6440"\w* creatures \w went|strong="H3212"\w* \w straight|strong="H5676"\w* \w ahead|strong="H6440"\w* \w in|strong="H3212"\w* whatever \w direction|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w spirit|strong="H7307"\w*\add that controlled/guided them\add* wanted \w them|strong="H6440"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w go|strong="H3212"\w*, \w without|strong="H3808"\w* changing \w directions|strong="H6440"\w* \w while|strong="H1961"\w* \w they|strong="H8033"\w* \w were|strong="H1961"\w* moving.  
\v 13 \w The|strong="H4480"\w*\add four\add* \w creatures|strong="H2416"\w* \w resembled|strong="H1823"\w* \w burning|strong="H1197"\w* \w coals|strong="H1513"\w* \w or|strong="H4480"\w* \w torches|strong="H3940"\w*. \w A|strong="H3068"\w* blazing \w fire|strong="H1513"\w* \w moved|strong="H1980"\w* \w back|strong="H1980"\w* \w and|strong="H1980"\w* \w forth|strong="H3318"\w* \w among|strong="H4480"\w* \w the|strong="H4480"\w* \w creatures|strong="H2416"\w*, \w and|strong="H1980"\w* lighting \w flashed|strong="H1980"\w* \w from|strong="H4480"\w* \w among|strong="H4480"\w* \w them|strong="H3318"\w*.  
\v 14 \w The|strong="H7725"\w* \w creatures|strong="H2416"\w* moved \w back|strong="H7725"\w* \w and|strong="H7725"\w* forth\add extremely rapidly\add*, \w like|strong="H4758"\w* [SIM] flashes \w of|strong="H4758"\w* lightning.   
\p
\v 15 \w While|strong="H2009"\w* \w I|strong="H2009"\w* \w looked|strong="H7200"\w* \w at|strong="H7200"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* four \w living|strong="H2416"\w* \w creatures|strong="H2416"\w*, \w I|strong="H2009"\w* \w saw|strong="H7200"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* wheel \w on|strong="H7200"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w ground|strong="H6440"\w* beside each \w of|strong="H6440"\w* \w them|strong="H6440"\w*.  
\v 16 Each \w of|strong="H5869"\w* \w the|strong="H8432"\w* wheels \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H8432"\w* \w same|strong="H8432"\w*, \w and|strong="H5869"\w* they all shone \w like|strong="H1961"\w* [SIM] ◄chrysolite/\w a|strong="H3068"\w* valuable green stone►. Each \w seemed|strong="H5869"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w have|strong="H1961"\w* \w one|strong="H1961"\w* wheel \w inside|strong="H8432"\w* \w another|strong="H8432"\w* wheel.  
\v 17 Whenever \w they|strong="H3808"\w* moved, \w they|strong="H3808"\w* would \w go|strong="H3212"\w* straight \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w one|strong="H3808"\w* \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* four \w directions|strong="H7253"\w* \w that|strong="H3808"\w* \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w faced|strong="H5437"\w*; \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w did|strong="H3808"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w turn|strong="H5437"\w*\add in another direction\add* \w while|strong="H5921"\w* \w they|strong="H3808"\w* moved.  
\v 18 \w The|strong="H5439"\w* \w rims|strong="H1354"\w* \w of|strong="H5869"\w* \w the|strong="H5439"\w* wheels \w were|strong="H1992"\w* covered \w with|strong="H5869"\w* \w eyes|strong="H5869"\w*.   
\p
\v 19 Whenever \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w living|strong="H2416"\w* \w creatures|strong="H2416"\w* moved, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* wheels moved \w with|strong="H5921"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w*. \add So\add* whenever \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w creatures|strong="H2416"\w* \w rose|strong="H5375"\w* \w from|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* ground, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* wheels\add also\add* \w rose|strong="H5375"\w* \w up|strong="H5375"\w*.  
\v 20 \w Wherever|strong="H8033"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w spirit|strong="H7307"\w*\add that controlled the creatures\add* wanted \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w creatures|strong="H2416"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w go|strong="H3212"\w*, \w they|strong="H3588"\w* \w went|strong="H3212"\w*, \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* wheels \w went|strong="H3212"\w* \w with|strong="H5921"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w*, \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w spirit|strong="H7307"\w*\add that controlled/guided them\add* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* wheels [DOU].  
\v 21 \w Whenever|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w creatures|strong="H2416"\w* \w moved|strong="H7307"\w*, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* wheels \w moved|strong="H7307"\w*. \w Whenever|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w creatures|strong="H2416"\w* \w stood|strong="H5975"\w*\add still\add*, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* wheels \w stopped|strong="H5975"\w*. \w Whenever|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w creatures|strong="H2416"\w* \w rose|strong="H5375"\w* \w up|strong="H5375"\w* \w from|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* ground, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* wheels \w rose|strong="H5375"\w* \w up|strong="H5375"\w* \w with|strong="H5921"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w*.   
\p
\v 22 \w Above|strong="H4605"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w heads|strong="H7218"\w* \w of|strong="H7218"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w creatures|strong="H2416"\w* there \w was|strong="H7218"\w* \w something|strong="H1823"\w* \w that|strong="H2416"\w* \w resembled|strong="H1823"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* dome. \w It|strong="H5921"\w* shone \w like|strong="H1823"\w* \w ice|strong="H7140"\w* (\w OR|strong="H3068"\w*, \w crystal|strong="H7140"\w*) shines, \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w it|strong="H5921"\w* \w was|strong="H7218"\w* \w awesome|strong="H3372"\w*.  
\v 23 \w Under|strong="H8478"\w* \w the|strong="H8478"\w* dome, \w the|strong="H8478"\w* creatures stretched \w out|strong="H8147"\w* \w their|strong="H3680"\w* \w wings|strong="H3671"\w*. \w Each|strong="H8147"\w* \w one|strong="H3671"\w* \w had|strong="H2007"\w* \w two|strong="H8147"\w* \w wings|strong="H3671"\w*; \add each wing\add* stretched towards \w the|strong="H8478"\w* creature \w that|strong="H7549"\w*\add was next to\add* \w it|strong="H3680"\w*, \w and|strong="H8147"\w* \w two|strong="H8147"\w* \w wings|strong="H3671"\w* \w that|strong="H7549"\w* \w were|strong="H3671"\w* against \w the|strong="H8478"\w* creature’s \w body|strong="H1472"\w*.  
\v 24 Whenever \w the|strong="H8085"\w* creatures moved, \w their|strong="H8085"\w* \w wings|strong="H3671"\w* \w made|strong="H5975"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w sound|strong="H6963"\w* \w that|strong="H8085"\w* resembled \w the|strong="H8085"\w* roar \w made|strong="H5975"\w* \w by|strong="H5975"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* rushing \w stream|strong="H4325"\w*. \w It|strong="H5975"\w* \w also|strong="H8085"\w* \w sounded|strong="H8085"\w* \w like|strong="H7227"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* \w voice|strong="H6963"\w* \w of|strong="H6963"\w* \w Almighty|strong="H7706"\w* God, \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w like|strong="H7227"\w* [SIM] \w the|strong="H8085"\w* \w noise|strong="H6963"\w* \w of|strong="H6963"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w huge|strong="H7227"\w* \w army|strong="H4264"\w* marching. Whenever \w the|strong="H8085"\w* creatures \w stood|strong="H5975"\w* \w still|strong="H5975"\w*\add on the ground\add*, \w they|strong="H8085"\w* lowered \w their|strong="H8085"\w* \w wings|strong="H3671"\w*.   
\p
\v 25 \w While|strong="H1961"\w* \w they|strong="H5921"\w* \w stood|strong="H5975"\w*\add on the ground\add* \w with|strong="H5921"\w* \w their|strong="H5921"\w* \w wings|strong="H3671"\w* lowered, \w there|strong="H1961"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w voice|strong="H6963"\w* \w from|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* dome \w that|strong="H1961"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w over|strong="H5921"\w* \w their|strong="H5921"\w* \w heads|strong="H7218"\w*.  
\v 26 \w Above|strong="H4605"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* dome \w was|strong="H7218"\w* \w something|strong="H4758"\w* \w that|strong="H7549"\w* \w resembled|strong="H1823"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w*\add huge\add* \w throne|strong="H3678"\w*\add that was made of a huge\add* ◄\w sapphire|strong="H5601"\w*/valuable blue \w stone|strong="H5601"\w*►. Sitting \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w throne|strong="H3678"\w* \w was|strong="H7218"\w* someone \w that|strong="H7549"\w* \w resembled|strong="H1823"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* human.  
\v 27 \w I|strong="H7200"\w* \w saw|strong="H7200"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w above|strong="H4605"\w* \w his|strong="H7200"\w* \w waist|strong="H4975"\w* \w his|strong="H7200"\w* \w body|strong="H4975"\w* resembled \w metal|strong="H2830"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w was|strong="H1004"\w* \w glowing|strong="H2830"\w* \w as|strong="H1004"\w* though \w it|strong="H7200"\w* \w had|strong="H5869"\w*\add a very hot\add* fire \w inside|strong="H1004"\w* \w it|strong="H7200"\w*. \w And|strong="H1004"\w* \w I|strong="H7200"\w* \w saw|strong="H7200"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w below|strong="H4295"\w* \w his|strong="H7200"\w* \w waist|strong="H4975"\w* \w there|strong="H7200"\w* \w was|strong="H1004"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w very|strong="H4605"\w* brilliant \w light|strong="H5051"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w surrounded|strong="H5439"\w* \w him|strong="H7200"\w*.  
\v 28 \w It|strong="H1931"\w*\add shone\add* \w like|strong="H1961"\w* [SIM] \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w rainbow|strong="H7198"\w* shines \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w clouds|strong="H6051"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w rainy|strong="H1653"\w* \w day|strong="H3117"\w*.  
\p \w That|strong="H7200"\w* \w was|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* brilliant \w light|strong="H5051"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* represented \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w presence|strong="H6440"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*. \w When|strong="H1961"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w saw|strong="H7200"\w* \w it|strong="H1931"\w*, \w I|strong="H3117"\w* prostrated myself \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w ground|strong="H6440"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w heard|strong="H8085"\w* \w him|strong="H6440"\w* \w speak|strong="H1696"\w*.   
\c 2  
\s1 Ezekiel was called to be a prophet  
\p
\v 1 \w He|strong="H5921"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w*, “\w You|strong="H5921"\w* human, \w stand|strong="H5975"\w* \w up|strong="H5975"\w* \w while|strong="H5921"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w speak|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w*.”  
\v 2 \w While|strong="H5921"\w* \w he|strong="H5921"\w* \w spoke|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w*, \add God’s\add* \w Spirit|strong="H7307"\w* \w entered|strong="H5975"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w* \w and|strong="H8085"\w* enabled \w me|strong="H5921"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w stand|strong="H5975"\w* \w up|strong="H5975"\w*. \w Then|strong="H1696"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w heard|strong="H8085"\w* \w him|strong="H5921"\w* \w speak|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w*.   
\p
