\v 22  \add I felt\add* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w take|strong="H3318"\w* \w control|strong="H3027"\w* [MTY] \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w*, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w he|strong="H8033"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w*, “\w Get|strong="H6965"\w* \w up|strong="H6965"\w* \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w go|strong="H3318"\w* \w out|strong="H3318"\w*\add from the city down\add* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w plain|strong="H1237"\w*/\w valley|strong="H1237"\w*, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w there|strong="H8033"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w speak|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w*.”  
