\c 4  
\s1 Ezekiel symbolized the coming destruction of Jerusalem  
\p
\v 1  \add Yahweh also said to me,\add* “\w You|strong="H5414"\w* human, \w take|strong="H3947"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* large clay tablet/\w brick|strong="H3843"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w put|strong="H5414"\w* \w it|strong="H5414"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w front|strong="H6440"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w*. \w Then|strong="H3947"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* clay\add engrave/draw\add* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w it|strong="H5414"\w* lines \w that|strong="H5414"\w* represent \w Jerusalem|strong="H3389"\w*.  
\v 2 \w Then|strong="H5414"\w*\add draw figures around it to represent enemy soldiers who will\add* \w surround|strong="H5439"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* city. \w Make|strong="H7760"\w* mounds \w around|strong="H5439"\w* \w it|strong="H5414"\w* \w and|strong="H4264"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* dirt \w ramp|strong="H5550"\w* \w up|strong="H5414"\w* \w against|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w wall|strong="H1785"\w*\add around the city\add*. \w Set|strong="H7760"\w*\add figures around it that represent\add* ◄\w battering|strong="H3733"\w* \w rams|strong="H3733"\w*/heavy \w logs|strong="H1129"\w* \w that|strong="H5414"\w* \w will|strong="H5414"\w* break though \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w walls|strong="H1785"\w*►.  
\v 3 \w Then|strong="H1961"\w* \w take|strong="H3947"\w* \w an|strong="H1961"\w* \w iron|strong="H1270"\w* \w pan|strong="H4227"\w*, \w and|strong="H3478"\w* \w place|strong="H5414"\w* \w it|strong="H5414"\w* \add to be\add* \w like|strong="H1961"\w* \w an|strong="H1961"\w* \w iron|strong="H1270"\w* \w wall|strong="H7023"\w* \w between|strong="H5921"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* \w and|strong="H3478"\w*\add the drawing of\add* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w city|strong="H5892"\w*. \w Then|strong="H1961"\w* \w turn|strong="H5414"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* \w face|strong="H6440"\w* \w toward|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* drawing. \w It|strong="H5414"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* symbolize \w that|strong="H1931"\w*\add enemy troops will\add* surround \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w city|strong="H5892"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w attack|strong="H6696"\w* \w it|strong="H5414"\w*. \w That|strong="H1931"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* warning \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* Israeli \w people|strong="H1931"\w* [MTY].   
\p
\v 4-5 Then lie on your left side, and stay like that for 390 days. That will\add symbolize that the Israeli people will be punished for\add* their sins; you must lie like that one day for each year during which they will be punished.   
\p
\v 6 \w After|strong="H5921"\w* \w that|strong="H3117"\w*, \w lie|strong="H7901"\w* \w down|strong="H7901"\w* \w again|strong="H8145"\w*. \w This|strong="H5414"\w* \w time|strong="H3117"\w*, \w lie|strong="H7901"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* right \w side|strong="H6654"\w* \w for|strong="H5921"\w* 40 \w days|strong="H3117"\w*. \w That|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H1004"\w*\add symbolize that the Israeli people will be punished more\add* \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w their|strong="H5375"\w* \w sins|strong="H5771"\w*, \w one|strong="H5375"\w* \w day|strong="H3117"\w* \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w each|strong="H3117"\w* \w year|strong="H8141"\w*\add during which they will be punished\add*.  
