\v 12 Eat \w that|strong="H1931"\w* \w bread|strong="H5692"\w* \w like|strong="H5869"\w* \w you|strong="H5869"\w* would eat \w a|strong="H3068"\w* loaf \w of|strong="H5869"\w* \w barley|strong="H8184"\w* \w bread|strong="H5692"\w*. \w But|strong="H1931"\w* \w use|strong="H1931"\w* \w your|strong="H5869"\w* \w own|strong="H5869"\w* dried \w dung|strong="H1561"\w* \w for|strong="H5869"\w* fuel \w to|strong="H5869"\w* \w bake|strong="H5746"\w* \w the|strong="H5869"\w* \w bread|strong="H5692"\w* \w while|strong="H1931"\w* \w people|strong="H1931"\w* \w are|strong="H5869"\w* \w watching|strong="H5869"\w*.  
