\s1 The people of Jerusalem are like useless grapevines  
\p
\v 1 \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w gave|strong="H1961"\w* \w me|strong="H1697"\w* another \w message|strong="H1697"\w*. \add He said\add*,  
\v 2 “\w You|strong="H3605"\w* human, \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w wood|strong="H6086"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* grapevine \w is|strong="H4100"\w* certainly \w not|strong="H1961"\w* [RHQ] \w more|strong="H1961"\w* useful \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w branches|strong="H2156"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w trees|strong="H6086"\w* \w in|strong="H1121"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w forest|strong="H3293"\w*.  
