\v 6 \w Therefore|strong="H3651"\w*, \w this|strong="H3651"\w* \w is|strong="H3651"\w* \w what|strong="H3541"\w* \add I\add*, \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3069"\w*, say: \w The|strong="H5414"\w* \w wood|strong="H6086"\w* \w of|strong="H3427"\w* grapevines \w is|strong="H3651"\w* useful only \w for|strong="H3427"\w* fuel \w in|strong="H3427"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* fire. Similarly, \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \w people|strong="H3427"\w* \w who|strong="H3427"\w* \w live|strong="H3427"\w* \w in|strong="H3427"\w* \w Jerusalem|strong="H3389"\w*\add are useless\add*.  
