\v 43 \w And|strong="H6440"\w* \w there|strong="H8033"\w*\add in Israel\add* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w will|strong="H6213"\w* \w remember|strong="H2142"\w* \w how|strong="H2142"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* conducted \w your|strong="H3605"\w* lives \add previously, you will remember\add* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w actions|strong="H5949"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w caused|strong="H6213"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w become|strong="H2930"\w* unacceptable \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w*, \w and|strong="H6440"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w will|strong="H6213"\w* hate/despise \w yourselves|strong="H2930"\w* \w for|strong="H6213"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w evil|strong="H7451"\w* \w things|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w have|strong="H3605"\w* \w done|strong="H6213"\w*.  
