\s1 Prophecy against the southern part of Israel  
\p
\v 45 \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* gave me another message. He said,  
\v 46 “You human, turn toward the south. Preach about what will happen to that dry land, to the forest there.  
\v 47 Say to the forest in the south\add part of Israel\add*: 'Listen to this message that \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* the Lord is saying \add about you\add*: “I am about to start \w a|strong="H3068"\w* fire in your midst, and it will burn up all your trees, \add both\add* the green trees and the withered/dry trees. Nothing will extinguish the blazing flames. And the fire will scorch the faces of everyone \add who lives\add* in that area, from the south to the north.  
\v 48 Everyone will see that it is I, \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*, who have lit this fire, and no one will \add be able to\add* put it out.” ' ”   
\p
\v 49 Then I said, “\w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*, my Lord, \add when I tell things like this to people, they do not believe me\add*. They say about me, ‘He is only telling parables.’ ”   
\c 21  
\s1 Yahweh will punish Israel  
\p
\v 1 \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w gave|strong="H1961"\w* \w me|strong="H1697"\w* another \w message|strong="H1697"\w*. \add He said,\add*  
\v 2 “\w You|strong="H6440"\w* human, \w turn|strong="H7760"\w* \w toward|strong="H1870"\w* Jerusalem. \w Preach|strong="H5197"\w* \w about|strong="H1870"\w* \w what|strong="H1870"\w* \w will|strong="H1121"\w* happen \w to|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* temple \add there\add*. \w Preach|strong="H5197"\w* \w about|strong="H1870"\w* \w what|strong="H1870"\w* \w will|strong="H1121"\w* happen \w to|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* Israeli \w people|strong="H1121"\w*.  
\v 3 \w Say|strong="H1697"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w them|strong="H6440"\w*, ‘\w This|strong="H3541"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w what|strong="H1697"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w says|strong="H3541"\w*: \w I|strong="H2005"\w* \w am|strong="H3068"\w* opposed \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w*.  
\v 4 \w So|strong="H3808"\w*\add what I will do to you will be as though\add* [MET] \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* pull \w my|strong="H3605"\w* sword \w from|strong="H3068"\w* \w its|strong="H3605"\w* sheath \add and strike you\add*. \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* kill \w everyone|strong="H3605"\w*, \w including|strong="H3605"\w* righteous \w people|strong="H1320"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* wicked \w people|strong="H1320"\w* [DOU]. \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* get rid \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w everyone|strong="H3605"\w*, \w from|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* south \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* north.  
\v 5 \w Then|strong="H3808"\w* everyone \w will|strong="H3808"\w* know \w that|strong="H1931"\w*\add it is as though\add* \w I|strong="H3808"\w*, \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*, \w have|strong="H3808"\w* struck \w people|strong="H3808"\w* \w with|strong="H1931"\w* \w my|strong="H3808"\w* sword, \w and|strong="H4912"\w* \w I|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* put \w it|strong="H1931"\w* back \w in|strong="H3808"\w* \w its|strong="H3808"\w* sheath again.’   
\p
\v 6 \w Therefore|strong="H3068"\w*, \w you|strong="H1697"\w* human, groan! Groan \w in|strong="H3068"\w* front \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* Israeli people very sadly \w and|strong="H3068"\w* sorrowfully [IDM, DOU].  
\v 7 \w And|strong="H1121"\w* \w when|strong="H1121"\w* \w they|strong="H3478"\w* ask \w you|strong="H6440"\w*, ‘Why \w are|strong="H1121"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* groaning?’ tell \w them|strong="H6440"\w*, ‘\w Because|strong="H6440"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* news \w that|strong="H3478"\w* \w they|strong="H3478"\w* soon \w will|strong="H3478"\w* hear. Everyone \w will|strong="H3478"\w* \w be|strong="H1121"\w* very fearful [IDM], \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w their|strong="H7760"\w* knees \w will|strong="H3478"\w* become \w as|strong="H3389"\w* weak \w as|strong="H3389"\w* [SIM] water. \add A great disaster\add* \w will|strong="H3478"\w* soon occur. \w That|strong="H3478"\w* \w is|strong="H3478"\w* what \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* Lord \w is|strong="H3478"\w* promising.’”   
\p
\v 8 \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w gave|strong="H3318"\w* \w me|strong="H4480"\w* \w another|strong="H4480"\w* \w message|strong="H3068"\w*. \add He said\add*,  
