\q2 \w it|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* polished \w so|strong="H3808"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w it|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* flash \w like|strong="H3318"\w* lightning.  
