\v 15 \w In|strong="H1121"\w* \w order|strong="H4616"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w people|strong="H1121"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* very \w much|strong="H3605"\w* afraid [IDM]  
