\q2 \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \add then\add* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w no|strong="H3605"\w* longer \w be|strong="H1961"\w* angry.  
\q1 \add That will surely happen because\add* \w I|strong="H3588"\w*, \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*, \w have|strong="H1961"\w* \w said|strong="H3651"\w* \w it|strong="H1931"\w*.’”   
\s1 The sword of the King of Babylonia  
\p
\v 18 \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w gave|strong="H1961"\w* \w me|strong="H3808"\w* \w another|strong="H1571"\w* message. \add He said,\add*  
\v 19 “\w You|strong="H5221"\w* human, make\add a map\add*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w on|strong="H2719"\w* \w it|strong="H1931"\w* mark \w two|strong="H5221"\w* roads \w for|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H5221"\w* King \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Babylonia \w to|strong="H1121"\w* march \w on|strong="H2719"\w*\add along with his army, carrying\add* \w their|strong="H5221"\w* \w swords|strong="H2719"\w*. \w When|strong="H1121"\w* \w they|strong="H1931"\w* depart \w from|strong="H1121"\w* \w their|strong="H5221"\w* country, \w they|strong="H1931"\w* \w will|strong="H2719"\w* come \w to|strong="H1121"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* sign post where \w the|strong="H5221"\w* road divides.  
\v 20  \add If they continue on the one road,\add* \w they|strong="H5921"\w* \w will|strong="H2719"\w* attack Rabbah\add city\add*, \w the|strong="H3605"\w* capital \w of|strong="H8179"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* Ammon people-group. \add If they continue on the other road,\add* \w they|strong="H5921"\w* \w will|strong="H2719"\w* come \w to|strong="H5921"\w* Judah \w and|strong="H2719"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w Jerusalem|strong="H4616"\w*, \add a city\add* \w with|strong="H6213"\w* walls \w around|strong="H5921"\w* \w it|strong="H5414"\w*.  
\v 21  \add When the army of\add* Babylonia \w comes|strong="H6440"\w* \w to|strong="H6440"\w* where \w the|strong="H6440"\w* road divides, \add they will stop\add*, \w and|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w king|strong="H6440"\w* \w will|strong="H6440"\w* perform magic rituals \add to decide which road to go on\add*. \w He|strong="H6440"\w* \w will|strong="H6440"\w* \w throw|strong="H7760"\w* arrows; \add then\add* consult \w his|strong="H7760"\w* idols\add about which road to go on\add*, \w and|strong="H6440"\w* \w he|strong="H6440"\w* \w will|strong="H6440"\w* ◄examine/\w look|strong="H7760"\w* \w at|strong="H6440"\w*► \w the|strong="H6440"\w* liver\add of a sheep\add*.  
\v 22 \w With|strong="H3068"\w* \w his|strong="H3068"\w* \w right|strong="H3068"\w* \w hand|strong="H3709"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* pick up \w the|strong="H5221"\w* arrow marked ‘Jerusalem’. \w He|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w then|strong="H1696"\w*\add command his soldiers to go to Jerusalem. When they arrive there, they\add* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w set|strong="H5117"\w* up ◄rams/devices \w to|strong="H1696"\w* batter\add down the walls\add*,► \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \add then\add* \w the|strong="H5221"\w* king \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w give|strong="H5117"\w* \w the|strong="H5221"\w* command \w for|strong="H3068"\w* \w them|strong="H5221"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w slaughter|strong="H5221"\w* \add the people\add*. \w They|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* shout \add a battle-cry\add*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w they|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w set|strong="H5117"\w* up \w the|strong="H5221"\w* rams \w against|strong="H1696"\w* \w the|strong="H5221"\w* \add city\add* gates. \w They|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* build \w a|strong="H3068"\w* dirt ramp \add against the walls around the city\add*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w set|strong="H5117"\w* up things \w to|strong="H1696"\w* bash \w those|strong="H1696"\w* walls.  
\v 23 \w The|strong="H3068"\w* people\add in Jerusalem\add* \w who|strong="H3068"\w* \w had|strong="H3068"\w* \w promised|strong="H3068"\w* \add to be loyal to the King of Babylonia will think that those rituals must be wrong. They will think that his army should not be attacking them\add*. \w But|strong="H1961"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* remind \w them|strong="H1961"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* sins [MTY] \w that|strong="H3068"\w* \w they|strong="H3068"\w* \w had|strong="H3068"\w* \w committed|strong="H1961"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w*\add his army\add* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* capture \w them|strong="H1961"\w*.   
\p
\v 24 Therefore, \add tell the Israeli people that\add* \w this|strong="H3027"\w* \w is|strong="H3027"\w* \w what|strong="H1870"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H7760"\w* Lord says: ‘\w You|strong="H7760"\w* \w people|strong="H1121"\w* \w have|strong="H1121"\w* allowed everyone \w to|strong="H3318"\w* see \w that|strong="H4428"\w* \w you|strong="H7760"\w* \w are|strong="H1121"\w* openly rebelling\add against the King of Babylonia\add*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w by|strong="H3027"\w* \w doing|strong="H1870"\w* \w that|strong="H4428"\w* \w you|strong="H7760"\w* \w have|strong="H1121"\w* shown \w that|strong="H4428"\w* everything \w that|strong="H4428"\w* \w you|strong="H7760"\w* \w do|strong="H1870"\w* \w is|strong="H3027"\w* sinful. Therefore \w you|strong="H7760"\w* \w will|strong="H4428"\w* \w be|strong="H3027"\w* captured \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w taken|strong="H7760"\w*\add to Babylonia\add*.’   
\p
\v 25 \w Also|strong="H1121"\w*, say, ‘\w You|strong="H7760"\w* very wicked [DOU] king \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Israel, \w it|strong="H7760"\w* \w is|strong="H1870"\w* \w your|strong="H7760"\w* time\add to die\add*. \w It|strong="H7760"\w* \w is|strong="H1870"\w* \w the|strong="H7760"\w* time \w for|strong="H3389"\w* \w you|strong="H7760"\w* \w to|strong="H3389"\w* \w be|strong="H1121"\w* punished.’  
\v 26 \w And|strong="H4428"\w* \w this|strong="H7200"\w* \w is|strong="H1870"\w* \w what|strong="H7200"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* Lord says \add to you soldiers from Babylonia\add*: ‘\w Take|strong="H5975"\w* \w off|strong="H4428"\w* \add the king’s\add* turban \w and|strong="H4428"\w* \w his|strong="H7200"\w* crown, \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w now|strong="H3588"\w* \w things|strong="H8147"\w* \w will|strong="H4428"\w* \w be|strong="H4428"\w* different \w than|strong="H3588"\w* \w they|strong="H3588"\w* \w were|strong="H4428"\w* \add before\add*. \w Those|strong="H7080"\w*\add in Jerusalem\add* \w who|strong="H4428"\w* \w had|strong="H4428"\w* \w no|strong="H7200"\w* authority \w will|strong="H4428"\w* \w now|strong="H3588"\w* \w be|strong="H4428"\w* given authority, \w and|strong="H4428"\w* \w those|strong="H7080"\w* \w who|strong="H4428"\w* \w had|strong="H4428"\w* authority \w will|strong="H4428"\w* \w have|strong="H7200"\w* \w their|strong="H7200"\w* authority taken \w from|strong="H7200"\w* \w them|strong="H5975"\w*.  
\v 27  \add Jerusalem\add* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* completely ruined. \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w cause|strong="H6310"\w* \w it|strong="H7760"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* ruined, \w and|strong="H6963"\w* \w it|strong="H7760"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w not|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \w rebuilt|strong="H1129"\w*/\w restored|strong="H1129"\w* \w until|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w king|strong="H5921"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* whom \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w city|strong="H8179"\w* truly \w belongs|strong="H1961"\w* \w comes|strong="H1961"\w*; \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w give|strong="H7760"\w* \w it|strong="H7760"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w him|strong="H5921"\w*\add to rule it\add*.’ ”   
\s1 A prophecy about Ammon  
\p
\v 28 “\w And|strong="H5869"\w*, \w you|strong="H5869"\w* human, prophesy \w and|strong="H5869"\w* say \add this\add*: '\w This|strong="H1931"\w* \w is|strong="H1931"\w* \w what|strong="H2142"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H2142"\w* Lord says \w about|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H2142"\w* Ammon people-group, \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w about|strong="H1961"\w* \w what|strong="H2142"\w* \w they|strong="H1931"\w* \w have|strong="H1961"\w* said \w to|strong="H1961"\w* insult \add Israel\add*:  
\q1 \add “The King of Babylon says,\add*  
\p ‘\add My soldiers have\add* swords’ [APO];  
\q2 \w they|strong="H1931"\w* \w have|strong="H1961"\w* pulled \w out|strong="H2142"\w* \w those|strong="H1931"\w* swords \w to|strong="H1961"\w* slaughter many \w people|strong="H5869"\w*.  
\q1 \w They|strong="H1931"\w* \w have|strong="H1961"\w* polished \w them|strong="H8610"\w* \w in|strong="H5869"\w* order \w to|strong="H1961"\w* kill \w people|strong="H5869"\w*,  
\q2 \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w make|strong="H2142"\w* \w those|strong="H1931"\w* swords flash \w like|strong="H1961"\w* lightning.   
\q1
\v 29  \add Your prophets\add* \w have|strong="H5771"\w* given \w you|strong="H3605"\w* false \w visions|strong="H7200"\w* \w about|strong="H3541"\w* \add what will happen to\add* \w you|strong="H3605"\w*,  
\q2 \w and|strong="H7200"\w* \w they|strong="H3651"\w* \w have|strong="H5771"\w* given \w you|strong="H3605"\w* messages \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w are|strong="H6588"\w* \w not|strong="H7200"\w* \w true|strong="H3651"\w*.  
\q1 \w So|strong="H3651"\w* swords \w will|strong="H3069"\w* strike \w the|strong="H3605"\w* necks  
\q2 \w of|strong="H3709"\w* \w those|strong="H3605"\w* wicked \w people|strong="H7200"\w*;  
\q1 \w it|strong="H3651"\w* \w is|strong="H3651"\w* time \w for|strong="H3605"\w* \w them|strong="H8610"\w* \w to|strong="H1540"\w* \w be|strong="H8610"\w* killed;  
\q2 \w it|strong="H3651"\w* \w is|strong="H3651"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* day \w when|strong="H7200"\w* \w they|strong="H3651"\w* \w will|strong="H3069"\w* \w be|strong="H8610"\w* punished\add for their sins\add*.   
\q1
\v 30 \w You|strong="H3117"\w* \w must|strong="H3478"\w* \w put|strong="H7563"\w* \w your|strong="H3117"\w* swords back \w in|strong="H3478"\w* \w their|strong="H3117"\w* sheaths  
\q2 \add because the days for you to slaughter your enemies are ended\add*.  
\q2 \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H3478"\w* judge those \w people|strong="H7563"\w* \w in|strong="H3478"\w* \w the|strong="H3117"\w* country where \w they|strong="H3117"\w* \w were|strong="H3478"\w* born.   
\q1
\v 31 \w I|strong="H3541"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* pour \w out|strong="H5493"\w* \w my|strong="H5493"\w* punishment [MTY] \w on|strong="H3069"\w* \w them|strong="H5493"\w*.  
\q1 Because \w I|strong="H3541"\w* am \w very|strong="H1364"\w* angry \w with|strong="H7311"\w* \w them|strong="H5493"\w*,  
\q2 \w my|strong="H5493"\w* breath \w on|strong="H3069"\w* \w them|strong="H5493"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* scorch \w them|strong="H5493"\w* \add like\add*\w a|strong="H3068"\w* fire [MET].  
\q1 \w I|strong="H3541"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* allow brutal men \w to|strong="H3808"\w* capture \w them|strong="H5493"\w*,  
\q2 men \w who|strong="H5493"\w* \w are|strong="H3808"\w* experts \w in|strong="H5493"\w* killing \w people|strong="H3808"\w*.   
\q1
\v 32 \w You|strong="H5414"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \add like\add* fuel [MET] \add that is burned\add* \w in|strong="H5414"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* fire.  
\q2 \w Your|strong="H5414"\w* blood \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \w shed|strong="H7760"\w* \w in|strong="H5414"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* \w own|strong="H1961"\w* land.  
\q1 \w No|strong="H3808"\w* \w one|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* remember \w you|strong="H5414"\w* \w any|strong="H5414"\w* \w more|strong="H3808"\w*.  
\q2 \add That will surely happen because\add* \w I|strong="H5414"\w*, \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*, \w have|strong="H1961"\w* said \w it|strong="H5414"\w*.” ' ”   
\c 22  
\s1 The sins of the people of Jerusalem  
\p
\v 1 \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w gave|strong="H1961"\w* \w me|strong="H1697"\w* another \w message|strong="H1697"\w*. \w He|strong="H3068"\w* \w said|strong="H1697"\w*,  
\v 2 “\w You|strong="H3605"\w* human, \w are|strong="H1121"\w* \w you|strong="H3605"\w* ready \w to|strong="H1121"\w* \w condemn|strong="H8199"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w people|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Jerusalem? \w It|strong="H3045"\w* \w is|strong="H3605"\w* [RHQ] \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w city|strong="H5892"\w* \w full|strong="H3605"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* murderers [MTY]. Remind \w them|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w detestable|strong="H8441"\w* \w things|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H3045"\w* \w they|strong="H3605"\w* \w have|strong="H3045"\w* \w done|strong="H3605"\w*.  
\v 3  \add Then\add* say, ‘\w This|strong="H6213"\w* \w is|strong="H5892"\w* \w what|strong="H6213"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3069"\w* \w says|strong="H3541"\w*: \w By|strong="H5921"\w* \w your|strong="H5921"\w* murdering \w people|strong="H1818"\w* \w and|strong="H5892"\w* \w by|strong="H5921"\w* ◄\w defiling|strong="H2930"\w* \w yourselves|strong="H2930"\w*/\w making|strong="H6213"\w* \w yourselves|strong="H2930"\w* unacceptable \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w God|strong="H3069"\w*► \w by|strong="H5921"\w* \w making|strong="H6213"\w* \w idols|strong="H1544"\w*, \w you|strong="H5921"\w* \w people|strong="H1818"\w* \w of|strong="H5892"\w* \w this|strong="H6213"\w* \w city|strong="H5892"\w* [APO] \w have|strong="H5892"\w* \w brought|strong="H6213"\w* \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w yourselves|strong="H2930"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w time|strong="H6256"\w* \w when|strong="H6256"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w* \add will be destroyed\add*.  
\v 4 \w You|strong="H5414"\w* \w have|strong="H1471"\w* \w become|strong="H2930"\w* guilty \w by|strong="H5921"\w* \w doing|strong="H6213"\w* \w both|strong="H3605"\w* \w of|strong="H3117"\w* \w those|strong="H3605"\w* \w things|strong="H3605"\w* [DOU]. \w You|strong="H5414"\w* \w have|strong="H1471"\w* \w brought|strong="H7126"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w an|strong="H6213"\w* end \w your|strong="H3605"\w* \w time|strong="H3117"\w* \add to remain alive\add* [DOU]. \w Therefore|strong="H3651"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H1471"\w* \w cause|strong="H5414"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w become|strong="H2930"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* group whom \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \add people of other\add* \w nations|strong="H1471"\w* \w will|strong="H1471"\w* \w scorn|strong="H2781"\w*; \w they|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H1471"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* laugh \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* [DOU].  
\v 5 People \w in|strong="H7227"\w* countries \w that|strong="H4480"\w* \w are|strong="H7227"\w* \w near|strong="H7138"\w* \w you|strong="H4480"\w* \w and|strong="H8034"\w* people \w who|strong="H7350"\w* \w live|strong="H8034"\w* \w far|strong="H7350"\w* \w from|strong="H4480"\w* \w you|strong="H4480"\w* \w will|strong="H7227"\w* \w make|strong="H8034"\w* fun \w of|strong="H8034"\w* \w you|strong="H4480"\w*, \w because|strong="H4480"\w* \w your|strong="H4480"\w* city \w is|strong="H8034"\w* \w full|strong="H7227"\w* \w of|strong="H8034"\w* lawless people \w and|strong="H8034"\w* \w full|strong="H7227"\w* \w of|strong="H8034"\w* \w confusion|strong="H4103"\w*.   
\p
\v 6 Think \w about|strong="H1961"\w* \w how|strong="H2009"\w* each \w of|strong="H1818"\w* \w your|strong="H1961"\w* Israeli kings \w have|strong="H1961"\w* \w used|strong="H1961"\w* \w their|strong="H1961"\w* \w power|strong="H2220"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w cause|strong="H1961"\w* \w people|strong="H1818"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* murdered [MTY].  
\v 7 \w Your|strong="H6213"\w* people \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w not|strong="H6213"\w* respect/honor \w their|strong="H8432"\w* parents; \w they|strong="H6213"\w* have \w oppressed|strong="H3238"\w* \w foreigners|strong="H1616"\w*; \w they|strong="H6213"\w* \w mistreat|strong="H3238"\w* \w orphans|strong="H3490"\w* \w and|strong="H6213"\w* widows.  
\v 8 You despise \w my|strong="H2490"\w* \w sacred|strong="H6944"\w* places \w and|strong="H6944"\w* ◄dishonor/do not respect► \w the|strong="H2490"\w* \w Sabbath|strong="H7676"\w* days.  
\v 9 \w Among|strong="H8432"\w* \w you|strong="H6213"\w* \w are|strong="H6213"\w* \w men|strong="H6213"\w* \w who|strong="H6213"\w* tell \w lies|strong="H1961"\w* \w in|strong="H6213"\w* \w order|strong="H4616"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w cause|strong="H6213"\w* others \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \w executed|strong="H6213"\w* [MTY]. \w There|strong="H1961"\w* \w are|strong="H6213"\w* \w those|strong="H1961"\w* \w who|strong="H6213"\w* eat\add food offered to idols\add* \w at|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* hilltop \add shrines\add*, \w and|strong="H2022"\w* \w they|strong="H6213"\w* \w perform|strong="H6213"\w* disgusting sexual \w acts|strong="H6213"\w*.  
\v 10 There are men \w who|strong="H2931"\w* have sex \w with|strong="H6031"\w* \w their|strong="H1540"\w* father’s wives [EUP], \w and|strong="H2931"\w* men \w who|strong="H2931"\w* have sex \w with|strong="H6031"\w* women during \w their|strong="H1540"\w* monthly \w menstrual|strong="H5079"\w* periods.  
\v 11 There \w are|strong="H6213"\w* \w men|strong="H6213"\w* \w who|strong="H6213"\w* \w have|strong="H1323"\w* sex \w with|strong="H6213"\w* someone \w else|strong="H7453"\w*’s wife. Some \w men|strong="H6213"\w* \w have|strong="H1323"\w* sex \w with|strong="H6213"\w* \w their|strong="H6213"\w* \w daughters-in-law|strong="H3618"\w* \w or|strong="H7453"\w* \w with|strong="H6213"\w* \w their|strong="H6213"\w* sisters \w or|strong="H7453"\w* half-sisters.  
\v 12 There \w are|strong="H1818"\w* among \w you|strong="H3947"\w* \w men|strong="H3947"\w* \w who|strong="H7911"\w* \w accept|strong="H3947"\w* \w bribes|strong="H7810"\w* \w in|strong="H1818"\w* \w order|strong="H4616"\w* \w to|strong="H4616"\w* cause someone \w to|strong="H4616"\w* \w be|strong="H1818"\w* executed [MTY]. \w You|strong="H3947"\w* charge high \w interest|strong="H5392"\w* when \w you|strong="H3947"\w* lend \w people|strong="H1818"\w* money. \w You|strong="H3947"\w* become rich \w by|strong="H7453"\w* forcing \w people|strong="H1818"\w* \w to|strong="H4616"\w* \w give|strong="H3947"\w* \w you|strong="H3947"\w* money. \w And|strong="H1818"\w*\add the worst thing is that\add* \w you|strong="H3947"\w* \w have|strong="H3947"\w* \w forgotten|strong="H7911"\w* \w me|strong="H3947"\w*, \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H5002"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3069"\w*.   
\p
\v 13 \w So|strong="H6213"\w* \w I|strong="H2009"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* shake \w my|strong="H5921"\w* fists \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w show|strong="H6213"\w* \w that|strong="H6213"\w* \w I|strong="H2009"\w* \w am|strong="H1961"\w* angry \w with|strong="H6213"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w* \w because|strong="H5921"\w* \w of|strong="H8432"\w* \w your|strong="H5921"\w* stealing money \w from|strong="H5921"\w* \w people|strong="H1818"\w* \w and|strong="H6213"\w* murdering [MTY] \w people|strong="H1818"\w* \w who|strong="H5221"\w* live \w among|strong="H8432"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w*.  
\v 14 \w When|strong="H3117"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* finish\add punishing\add* \w you|strong="H3117"\w*, \w you|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w no|strong="H6213"\w* longer [RHQ] \w be|strong="H3027"\w* \w courageous|strong="H2388"\w*/brave [DOU]. \w I|strong="H3117"\w*, \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*, \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \add what I will do to you\add*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w it|strong="H6213"\w*.  
