\v 8 \w This|strong="H3541"\w* \w is|strong="H2009"\w* \add also\add* \w what|strong="H3541"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3069"\w* \w says|strong="H3541"\w*: “\add The people of \add* \w Moab|strong="H4124"\w*\add south of Ammon\add* \w and|strong="H3063"\w* \add the people of\add* \w Seir|strong="H8165"\w*\add south of Moab despised Israel and\add* said, ‘\w The|strong="H3605"\w* \w people|strong="H1471"\w* [MTY] \w of|strong="H1004"\w* Israel \w have|strong="H1471"\w* become\add as unimportant\add* \w as|strong="H3063"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w other|strong="H3605"\w* \w nations|strong="H1471"\w*!’  
