\v 8 \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \add I say to\add* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w mountains|strong="H2022"\w* \w in|strong="H3478"\w* \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* huge crops \w of|strong="H2022"\w* \w fruit|strong="H6529"\w* \w will|strong="H5971"\w* grow \w on|strong="H2022"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* trees \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w my|strong="H5414"\w* Israeli \w people|strong="H5971"\w*, \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w they|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H5971"\w* \w soon|strong="H3588"\w* return home \add from Babylonia\add*.  
