\p
\v 13 \w This|strong="H3541"\w* \w is|strong="H1961"\w* \w also|strong="H3541"\w* \w what|strong="H3541"\w* \w I|strong="H3541"\w*, \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3069"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3069"\w*, say \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w you|strong="H3282"\w*: \w People|strong="H1471"\w* say \w that|strong="H1471"\w* \add only a small amount of food is produced on your mountains, and as a result the people of Israel\add* die \w from|strong="H1471"\w* hunger.  
