\s1 A prophecy about being one nation with one king  
\p
\v 15 \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w gave|strong="H1961"\w* \w me|strong="H1697"\w* \add another\add* \w message|strong="H1697"\w*. \w He|strong="H3068"\w* \w said|strong="H1697"\w*,  
