\v 10 \w Fishermen|strong="H1728"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w stand|strong="H5975"\w* \w along|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* bank \add of the Dead Sea to catch fish\add*. \w From|strong="H5921"\w* \w En-Gedi|strong="H5872"\w* \add on the western side\add* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w En-Eglaim|strong="H5882"\w* \add on the eastern side\add* \w there|strong="H1961"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* places \add for fishermen\add* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w spread|strong="H4894"\w* \w their|strong="H5921"\w* fishing \w nets|strong="H2764"\w*. \w There|strong="H1961"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \w many|strong="H7227"\w* \w kinds|strong="H4327"\w* \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w fish|strong="H1710"\w*, \w like|strong="H1961"\w* \w there|strong="H1961"\w* \w are|strong="H7227"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* Mediterranean \w Sea|strong="H3220"\w*.  
