\v 12 \w Many|strong="H3808"\w* \w kinds|strong="H3605"\w* \w of|strong="H4325"\w* \w fruit|strong="H6529"\w* \w trees|strong="H6086"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w grow|strong="H5927"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w both|strong="H4480"\w* \w sides|strong="H2088"\w* \w of|strong="H4325"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w river|strong="H5158"\w*. \w Their|strong="H3605"\w* \w leaves|strong="H5929"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w wither|strong="H5034"\w*, \w and|strong="H6086"\w* \w they|strong="H1992"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w always|strong="H3605"\w* \w have|strong="H1961"\w* \w fruit|strong="H6529"\w*. \w They|strong="H1992"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w bear|strong="H3318"\w* \w fruit|strong="H6529"\w* \w every|strong="H3605"\w* \w month|strong="H2320"\w*, \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \add they will continually get water from\add* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w water|strong="H4325"\w* \add that comes \add* \w from|strong="H4480"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w temple|strong="H4720"\w*. \w Their|strong="H3605"\w* \w fruit|strong="H6529"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* good \w to|strong="H3318"\w* \w eat|strong="H3978"\w* \w and|strong="H6086"\w* \w their|strong="H3605"\w* \w leaves|strong="H5929"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \add good\add* \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w healing|strong="H8644"\w*.”   
\s1 The division of the land  
\p
\v 13  \add In the vision\add*, \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \add also\add* said \w this|strong="H3541"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* me: “\w Here|strong="H3541"\w* \w is|strong="H3478"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* list \w of|strong="H7626"\w* \w the|strong="H3069"\w* \w twelve|strong="H8147"\w* \w tribes|strong="H7626"\w* \w of|strong="H7626"\w* \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w* \w and|strong="H3478"\w* \w the|strong="H3069"\w* \w territory|strong="H1366"\w* \w that|strong="H3478"\w* \w each|strong="H3541"\w* \w tribe|strong="H7626"\w* \w must|strong="H3478"\w* \w receive|strong="H5157"\w*. \add The descendants of\add* \w Joseph|strong="H3130"\w* \w will|strong="H3478"\w* \w receive|strong="H5157"\w* \w two|strong="H8147"\w* \w portions|strong="H2256"\w*; \add the tribe of Levi will not receive any\add*.  
\v 14 \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w lifted|strong="H5375"\w* \w up|strong="H5375"\w* \w my|strong="H5414"\w* \w arm|strong="H3027"\w* \w and|strong="H3027"\w* solemnly declared \w to|strong="H5414"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* ancestors \w that|strong="H5414"\w* \w I|strong="H5414"\w* would \w give|strong="H5414"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* \w this|strong="H2063"\w* \w land|strong="H5159"\w* \w to|strong="H5414"\w* \w own|strong="H3027"\w* permanently. \add So divide the land equally among all of the other tribes\add*.   
\p
\v 15 \w These|strong="H2088"\w* \w will|strong="H6828"\w* \w be|strong="H1870"\w* \w the|strong="H4480"\w* boundaries \w of|strong="H1366"\w* \w the|strong="H4480"\w* \w land|strong="H1366"\w*:  
\li1 On the north side, \add it will extend\add* from the Mediterranean Sea east along the road to Hethlon, past Lebo-Hamath to Zedad,  
\v 16 to \add the cities of\add* Berothah and Sibraim, which are on the border between Damascus and Hamath. \add From there the boundary will extend\add* as far as\add the city of \add* Hazer-Hatticon, which is on the border of the Hauran \add region\add*.  
\v 17 So the boundary will extend from the \add Mediterranean\add* Sea to \add the city of\add* Hazar-Enan on the border between Hamath to the north and Damascus \add to the south\add*. That will be the northern boundary.   
\li1
\v 18 On the east side, the boundary \add will extend\add* between Hauran and Damascus, \add south\add* along the Jordan \add River\add* between the Gilead \add region\add* and the land of Israel, along the Dead Sea as far as \add the town of\add* Tamar. That will be the eastern boundary.   
\li1
\v 19 On the south side, the boundary will extend from Tamar \add southwest\add* to the springs near \add the town of\add* Meribah-Kadesh. Then \add the boundary will extend west\add* along the dry riverbed \add at the border\add* of Egypt to the Mediterranean Sea. That will be the southern boundary.   
\li1
\v 20 On the west side, the boundary will be the Mediterranean Sea, north to near Lebo-Hamath.   
